title: Conservatives Hardest Hit
author: VD
content_html:
Well, there goes that whole “all men are created equal, I don’t see color” dodge.

I now look forward to absolutely every single future conversation I will have with an equalitarian, particularly those of the conservative variety. The backpedaling promises to be epic.
